<section id=section-104129  class="section section--layout--hidden section--margin--no-margin">
  <div class="section__inner">
          <div class="layout layout--twocol">
          <div  class="layout__region layout__region--top">
        
        

<div class="title title--z-index--one">
  <h2>  
                    

<span class="title-item title-item--color--highlight--primary title-item--outline title-item--size--extra-large">
  &quot;Forward
</span>

  
                    

<span class="title-item title-item--color--highlight--secondary title-item--outline title-item--size--extra-large">
  together.
</span>

  
                    

<span class="title-item title-item--color--highlight--tertiary title-item--outline title-item--size--extra-large">
  Sonke
</span>

  
                    

<span class="title-item title-item--color--highlight--primary title-item--outline title-item--size--extra-large">
  siya
</span>

  
                    

<span class="title-item title-item--color--secondary title-item--outline title-item--size--extra-large">
  phambili&quot;.
</span>

</h2>
</div>

      </div>
    
          <div  class="layout__region layout__region--first">
                        

<section class="margin--top--small no--line divider">
    <hr class="divider--line">
</section>


<div class="wysiwyg size--narrow">
  

            <div class="text-long"><p>Spring has sprung and Stellenbosch University is celebrating something new, a budding and exciting digital reawakening. Like an acorn quietly holding the promise of a mighty oak, our brand-new website is full of potential, ready to grow and expand in the months ahead. This journey began several years ago, when we planted the seed for a reimagined online presence - and now it is branching and shooting leaves.&nbsp;</p><p>This first phase is just the beginning. You will see a fresh design, a responsive and user-focused experience and intuitive ways to explore our institutional information. But not every branch will be there yet. Some pages, features and sections will still be growing – refined and added to over time. Like great trees, our website will not grow overnight. But from day one, it has been designed to be accessible and welcoming and to develop into something truly exceptional.&nbsp;</p><p>We invite you to explore, engage and grow with us.</p></div>
      
</div>

      </div>
    
          <div  class="layout__region layout__region--second">
        

        
   

  

  
  
      
<div class="media-component media-component--rounded--bottom--right media--default">

                       

<div class="media media--type-image media--view-mode-media-paragraph">
  
        


                                                
